For example the [Oracle config page|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Connecting+JIRA+to+Oracle] states the following:

{quote}
The recommended encoding is AL32UTF8 (the Oracle equivalent of Unicode UTF-8).
{quote}

